      "tag": "1.4.1",
      "zip": "https://github.com/astrochili/defold-operator/archive/refs/tags/1.4.1.zip"
    },
    {
      "message": "- Changed default values of sensitivity and smoothness of camera rotation by mouse.\n- Changed mouse input reading from `dx/dy` to `screen_dx/dy` to become more independent of window size and aspect ratio.\n- Fixed #7, improved handling of zoom-changing input when camera is stopped by an obstacle.",
      "published_at": "2023-05-17T12:15:11Z",
      "tag": "1.4",
      "zip": "https://github.com/astrochili/defold-operator/archive/refs/tags/1.4.zip"
